PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?item ?itemLabel ?employees ?website WHERE {
  {
    ?item wdt:P1128 ?employees .
    ?item wdt:P856 ?website .
    FILTER ( ?employees > 500000 ) .
    ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q4830453 .
    ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?itemLabel ) = 'en' )
  } UNION {
    ?item wdt:P1128 ?employees .
    ?item wdt:P856 ?website .
    FILTER ( ?employees > 500000 ) .
    ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q891723 .
    ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?itemLabel ) = 'en' )
  } UNION {
    ?item wdt:P1128 ?employees .
    ?item wdt:P856 ?website .
    FILTER ( ?employees > 500000 ) .
    ?item wdt:P31 wd:Q6881511 .
    ?item rdfs:label ?itemLabel .
    FILTER ( LANG( ?itemLabel ) = 'en' )
  }
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?employees )
LIMIT 20

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?game ?gameLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q810986 wdt:P31 ?type .
  ?type rdfs:label ?gameLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?gameLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?club ?clubLabel WHERE {
  ?club wdt:P31 wd:Q476028 ; wdt:P17 wd:Q29 .
  ?club rdfs:label ?clubLabel .
  FILTER ( langMatches( lang( ?clubLabel ) , "en" ) )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?show ?showLabel WHERE {
  ?show wdt:P58 wd:Q25014 .
  ?show wdt:P31 wd:Q5398426 .
  ?show rdfs:label ?showLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?showLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?episode ?episodeLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q5274359 wdt:P527 ?episode .
  ?episode rdfs:label ?episodeLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?episodeLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?country ( COUNT( ?cave ) AS ?caveCount ) ( SAMPLE( ?label ) AS ?countryLabel ) WHERE {
  ?cave wdt:P31 wd:Q35509 .
  ?cave wdt:P131 ?country .
  ?country wdt:P31 wd:Q3624078 .
  ?country rdfs:label ?label .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = "en" )
}
GROUP BY ?country
HAVING ( ?caveCount > 10 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?caveCount )

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
SELECT ?start WHERE {
  wd:Q211 wdt:P463 wd:Q458 .
  ?statement ps:P463 wd:Q458 ; pq:P580 ?start .
}
